These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, fanta, sprite
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, pony, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | sprite | fanta |
| Pet        | rat | ferret   | bird | pony    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, romance, mystery, western
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, australian, polish, brazilian
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
3. the polish is in an odd position##4
4. the turkish is the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the australian is on the right of the polish##1
6. the turkish is the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | time-travel  | romance  | western |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | turkish | polish | australian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, mango, cabbage, apricot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, adventure, sports, satire
1. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
2. the person eating cabbage is in an even position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | apricot | cabbage | mango    | eggplant      |
| Movie-Genre   | sports        | satire     | zombie | adventure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, magic-tricks, singing, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, punk, electronic
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the fan of jazz and the fan of electronic##2
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | sudoku | puzzles | magic-tricks | singing |
| Music-Genre   | punk       | jazz   | r&b    | electronic  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, classical, reggae, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, canadian, dutch, british
1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the british##1
2. the canadian is the fan of gospel##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
5. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4
6. the chinese is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | soul    | reggae   | gospel       |
| Nationality   | chinese | british | dutch | canadian |

