.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, zombie, disaster, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indian, thai, spanish
1. the indian is in an even position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the indian##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
4. the british is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the thai is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster      | zombie | scientific | mystery |
| Nationality   | spanish | indian     | british  | thai  |

