.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel, crime, martial-arts
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, subway, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person watching documentary movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts | crime | time-travel    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | subway  | snowmobile     | skateboard |

