.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, bartender, dancer, security-guard
4 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, mouse, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the bartender##3
2. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
4. the security-guard is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the librarian is between the security-guard and the bartender##2
6. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the lizard is between the librarian and the owner of the mouse##2
8. the librarian is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | bartender | librarian      | security-guard | dancer |
| Pet   | rat  | ferret | lizard    | mouse            |

