.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pumpkin, asparagus, kale
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, horse, chinchilla
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
2. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the rabbit and the person eating asparagus##2
4. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating asparagus is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | kale | pumpkin   | broccoli | asparagus |
| Pet    | chinchilla     | rabbit | goldfish     | horse  |

