.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate, 7up, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, metal, techno, pop
1. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the fan of pop is between the fan of punk and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | 7up   | mirinda | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | techno | metal | pop        | punk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, sprite, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton, handball, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | cola   | mirinda      | sprite      |
| Sport      | badminton | handball | weightlifting | skateboarding |

