.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pepper, mango, corn
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, folk, dubstep, d&b
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
4. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
5. the person eating mango is between the fan of folk and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | corn | pepper  | mango  | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | dubstep | techno | folk   |

