2. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
