.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, woodworking, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, biathlon, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's hobby is photography##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | reading | photography         | puzzles   | woodworking |
| Sport   | biathlon    | rugby | basketball | swimming   |

