.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, puzzles, drawing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, soccer, biathlon, rugby
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | hiking | puzzles    | drawing |
| Sport   | baseball   | biathlon  | rugby | soccer     |

