.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, collecting, card-games, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, canadian, brazilian
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
3. the colombian is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the colombian is between the brazilian and the canadian##2
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | reading   | card-games | photography | collecting    |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian  | brazilian     | chinese |

