.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, avocado, kiwi, cucumber
1. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person eating kiwi is in an even position##4
7. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | almond-milk    | juice       | sprite |
| Food       | avocado  | kiwi | cucumber | raspberry  |

