.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, malaysian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, helicopter, taxi
1. the japanese is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the japanese is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | malaysian | japanese  | egyptian |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | helicopter       | scooter | taxi     |

