.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, architect, dancer, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, roller, snowmobile, trike
1. the architect is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
3. the person driving the roller is between the journalist and the person driving the tram##2
4. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the chef##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | journalist | dancer   | chef | architect |
| Transport   | trike          | roller | tram         | snowmobile  |

 